退 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.應用陣法<br />\n2.組織隊伍<br />\n3.以大隊執行常規工作<br />\n4.以小隊執行專項工作</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先介紹四個基本陣式 <span style=\"color: red;\">柱 橫 箭 圓</span> 節錄於防暴教材<br />\n<br />\n前線玩家可動員群眾排陣作 進攻 防守 圍剿 及 正面受擊 應對<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">柱陣</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVdgjUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVdgjUk.png&h=794001b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一般用於隊伍穿插人群流動 群眾正面受遠程攻擊時佈下數個柱陣則可減少人群受擊之Surface Area<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">橫陣</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aFcXONP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaFcXONP.png&h=95ef6908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正面迎擊大數量敵意人士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">箭陣</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pwhONV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pwhONV.png&h=c73a1a49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用作重點突破重圍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">圓陣</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7dkVAs1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7dkVAs1.png&h=1088fd76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n向外: 四面受敵時用，保護平民及傷者 向內: 制服敵意人士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">行動動員</span></span><br />\n<br />\n派手帶記認<br />\n<br />\n有領導材能手足自行現場招募 以圖示<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">號碼</span></span>排列及分工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">行動決議半數反對 必須撤退 確保全員安全</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五個隊員職能</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GfJ8a1N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGfJ8a1N.png&h=d1c47abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10人編制 可加可減 需熟練以上陣列 確保行動零活<br />\n<br />\n以號碼作排位及分工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">左右各一</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1號</span></span> <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武</span></span><br />\n前線攻防<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2號</span></span> <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">防捕</span></span><br />\n二線snatch and grab back<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3號</span></span> <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">萬能俠</span></span><br />\n主要支援勇武及防捕 必要時無牌情況下為隊員基本急救<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4號</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">通訊</span></span><br />\n接收電子資訊 同時為逃生門提供準確資訊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5號</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">逃生門</span></span><br />\n計劃確保主次逃生路線可行 隊伍成員及附近手足全身而退<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">常規隊伍</span></span> <br />\n應用以上10人可加可減職能編制 齊備 <span style=\"color: red;\">勇武 防捕 萬能 通訊 逃生</span> 隊員 執行<span style=\"color: red;\">單一</span>主要工作，包括:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武梯隊</span></span><br />\n前線攻防<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">防捕梯隊</span></span><br />\n二線snatch and grab back<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">逃生門梯隊</span></span><br />\n計劃確保主次逃生路線可行 大隊手足全身而退 必要時組織殿後隊出計拖延追兵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新營地梯隊</span></span><br />\n遍地開花<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">物資管理梯隊</span></span><br />\n物資傳送及撤離<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">First Aid支援梯隊</span></span><br />\n保障First Aider安全及順利施救<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">小形隊伍</span></span><br />\n無須10人編制 群眾可自行發起，包括:<br />\n<br />\n(3-4人) <span style=\"color: red;\">折彈專家</span><br />\n處理及制止煙霧<br />\n<br />\n(2-3人) <span style=\"color: red;\">傳媒議員聯絡</span><br />\n主動引路求援 <br />\n<br />\n(5-6人) <span style=\"color: red;\">捉鬼敢死隊</span><br />\n偵察及妨礙敵意人士<br />\n<br />\n(2-3人) <span style=\"color: red;\">固定或流動哨站</span><br />\n配備望遠鏡偵察變數 2人作跑腿向群眾散布重要資訊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">備註</span><br />\n帶隊手足低調指揮 勿做箭把<br />\n10人共識行動可為運動散佈感染力<br />\n運動需要羣眾元素 不宜全體應用<br />\n只需少數有能前線apply 帶領現場手足<br />\n為前線增強動員能力 減低孤狼受傷風險<br />\n更上一層樓發揮Be Water<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">總結</span><br />\n4x陣式<br />\n5x隊員職能分工<br />\n6x常規隊伍<br />\n4x小形隊伍<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重新以上隊伍形式只識用於部分參與 切勿過份發揮 害死手足 Playbook為死 人為生 運動必須留有群眾游動力量 不宜過度聚焦人手 但群眾可以認識以上佈陣排列戰術 配合前線玩家</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光榮歸於義士<br />\n光榮歸於香港<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:09:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2a20cf7c7ffded2b5542a34c9af50febb56e932d","tid":1365941,"uid":287758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbad1d24ffb592d77aeac72fc3fc4f0125545c44","tid":1365941,"uid":287758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d72e13bb99e9fd360ae8c089859ca3516083bde1","tid":1365941,"uid":287758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5341ce063d7c1e0dc787af75e23bb4fa76f6481e","tid":1365941,"uid":116276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:54:24.000Z","msg":"喂實用 到時手足應該每隊有自己隊代號 例如大叫 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\